  <entry>
    <title>Python-基于元类实现一个ORM的demo</title>
    <link href="/2023/12/11/Python-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%83%E7%B1%BB%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAORM%E7%9A%84demo/"/>
    <url>/2023/12/11/Python-%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%83%E7%B1%BB%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAORM%E7%9A%84demo/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在 python 中，type 不仅可以用来获取变量的类型，还可以用来创建类对象。</p><p><img src="https://zhyclouds.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog/Pasted%20image%2020231211140642.png" alt="Pasted image 20231211140642"></p><p>在创建对象的时候其接收三个参数：</p><ul><li>类对象的名称</li><li>父类（元组）</li><li>属性、方法</li></ul><p>举个 demo：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, name, age, height</span>):  <br>    self.name = name  <br>    self.age = age  <br>    self.height = height  <br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建一个类对象</span><br>People = <span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;People&quot;</span>, (), &#123;  <br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;__init__&quot;</span>: __init__  <br>&#125;)  <br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建一个实例对象</span><br>stu1 = People(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;hy&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">19</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1.88</span>)  <br>  <br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(stu1.name)    <span class="hljs-comment"># hy  </span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(stu1.age)     <span class="hljs-comment"># 19  </span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(stu1.height)  <span class="hljs-comment"># 1.88</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>那么就有这样的一个关系，所有的类都是通过 type 进行创建的，所有的类默认是继承 Object 的，Object 类也是通过 type 进行创建的。</p><p>在类方法中，<code>__init__</code> 是在创建实例对象的时候调用的，还有一个 <code>__new__</code> 方法，是在这个类对象创建的时候才调用的，在 class 的参数中有一个 <code>metaclass</code> 元类，如果不传的话，默认就是使用 type 进行创建，也可以自定义，那么根据这个性质就能够自己实现一个简单的 ORM。</p><p>首先基于 type 类自己封装一个元类：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">DemoMetaClass</span>(<span class="hljs-title class_ inherited__">type</span>):  <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__new__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">cls, name, bases, attrs</span>):  <br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 在这里实现创建类的时候的逻辑  </span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># ...  </span><br>  <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>().__new__(cls, name, bases, attrs)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>定义一个 User 类：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">User</span>(metaclass=DemoMetaClass):  <br>    uid = (<span class="hljs-string">&quot;uid&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;int unsigned auto increment&quot;</span>)  <br>    username = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;username&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>    password = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;password&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>    email = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;email&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个 User 类在创建的时候会被 DemoMetaClass 拦截。</p><p>整体实现思路就是：<br>定义一个 Model 类，Model 类以及继承 Model 类的类在创建的时候会被元类拦截，在类属性里面设置上表名和字段的元组关系，Model 类有一个插入方法，在使用具体类创建实例对象的时候，会读取参数设置到属性中，接着读取属性和字段、表名拼接起来进行插入。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义元类  </span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ModelMetaclass</span>(<span class="hljs-title class_ inherited__">type</span>):  <br>  <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__new__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">cls, name, bases, attrs</span>):  <br>  <br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 定义一个映射字典  </span><br>        mappings = <span class="hljs-built_in">dict</span>()  <br>  <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> attr <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> attrs:  <br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">isinstance</span>(attrs[attr], <span class="hljs-built_in">tuple</span>):  <br>                mappings[attr] = attrs[attr]  <br>  <br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 将mappings字典保存到属性之中，进行返回给User类  </span><br>        attrs[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;__mappings__&#x27;</span>] = mappings  <br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 记录表名  </span><br>        attrs[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;__table__&#x27;</span>] = name  <br>  <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>.__new__(cls, name, bases, attrs)  <br>  <br>  <br><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义Model类  </span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Model</span>(metaclass=ModelMetaclass):  <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, **kwargs</span>):  <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> key, value <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> kwargs.items():  <br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">setattr</span>(self, key, value)  <br>  <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">save</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):  <br>        fields = []  <br>        args = []  <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> key, value <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> self.__mappings__.items():  <br>            fields.append(value[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>])  <br>            args.append(<span class="hljs-built_in">getattr</span>(self, key, <span class="hljs-literal">None</span>))  <br>  <br>        args_tmp = []  <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> value <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> args:  <br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">isinstance</span>(value, <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>):  <br>                args_tmp.append(<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(value))  <br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">isinstance</span>(value, <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>):  <br>                args_tmp.append(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;&#x27;%s&#x27;&quot;&quot;&quot;</span> % value)  <br>  <br>        sql = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;insert into %s(%s) values(%s)&quot;</span> % (self.__table__, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>.join(fields), <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>.join(args_tmp))  <br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;sql=&quot;</span>, sql)  <br>  <br>  <br><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义User类  </span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">User</span>(<span class="hljs-title class_ inherited__">Model</span>):  <br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 定义User表的字段以及字段类型  </span><br>    uid = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;uid&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;int unsigned&quot;</span>)  <br>    name = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;username&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>    email = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;email&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>    password = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;password&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>  <br>  <br><span class="hljs-comment"># 定义Student类  </span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Student</span>(<span class="hljs-title class_ inherited__">Model</span>):  <br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 定义字段映射关系  </span><br>    uid = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;uid&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;int unsigned&quot;</span>)  <br>    name = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;username&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>    classroom = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;room&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;varchar(30)&quot;</span>)  <br>  <br>  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span>():  <br>    u = User(uid=<span class="hljs-number">12345</span>, name=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Michael&#x27;</span>, email=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;test@orm.org&#x27;</span>, password=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;my-pwd&#x27;</span>)  <br>    u.save()  <br>  <br>    stu = Student(uid=<span class="hljs-number">123</span>, name=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fatboy&#x27;</span>, classroom=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;room1&#x27;</span>)  <br>    stu.save()  <br>  <br>  <br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:  <br>    main()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
